0.1.2 (2026.12.01)  Fix: exact name cache lookup now auto-uses cached stop, unless -R
                    Fix: selection by index gets auto used, no checks
                    Fix: full place list always shown before selecting stop
                    Fix: never auto-prompt when the name is ambiguous across multiple keys
                    Change: moved lookup logic away from _resolve_key into explicit match
                    Change: cleaned lookup_and_display flow and removed redundant checks
                    Fix: support for planes with color and naming
                    Fix: referencing of stops by index in list
                    Added support for multiple info/deletions at once, also by index
                    Added support for better help text with hints and usage message
                    Fix: json can now be empty
                    Fix: downgraded version number
                    Fix: showing all results, not only stops, when searching.
                    Fix: broke up function `lookup_and_display` into smaller methods

0.1.1 (2026.10.01)  Introduces argparse for proper CLI flags and help text
                    Added ferry and train as well as submodes (colors)
                    Broke out code into functions, preparing for modularization
                    Added multi-flag filtering (-bmtrf etc.)

0.1.0 (2026.10.01)  Basic functionality, geocoder and journey-planner API
